data.description:
Welcome to this thoughtfully designed single-level home nestled in the heart of Casa Grande. This charming property boasts four bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a sought after three-car garage, offering a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and modern living.
The home greets you with a welcoming facade, featuring well-maintained landscaping, and an inviting entryway.
Step into an open and airy interior, where the seamless flow between living spaces allows for comfortable daily living or entertaining. 
You will find 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 well-appointed bathrooms.  The kitchen has been tastefully updated with refreshed cabinets, granite counters, tile backsplash, and sleek black appliances! You will find neutral paint tones and charming decorator touches throughout.  The HVAC system is only 2 years old!  
You will spend much of your time in this inviting backyard where you will find lush grass perfect for the kids or pets, a spacious covered patio, and a gazebo allowing for even more entertaining space!
A spacious three-car garage not only provides ample parking but also offers additional storage space for outdoor equipment, recreational gear, or hobby supplies.
The pride of ownership in this home is evident and you will feel it as soon as you step inside.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this home!
